metadata.name: MunRaxixe Genesis 1/432
metadata.description:
This NFT is a compendium of 9 Rap songs by Yanick Jannotti that were never released on web2 and are now immortalized onchain. They are raw versions that are part of different moments of his career between 2016 and 2021 of his old Musical Collective called Akorja, in Brazil.

Rhyming in Portuguese, exploring boom bap and trap with all versatility, starting with the energy up there and ending with a very smooth vibe.

All images are from Paraty, Brazil.

Genesis marks the birth of MunRaxixe as his alter ego for web3

Holders will have airdrops, special access to physical events, and youtube royalties will be split between all tokens in the future.

Youtube Link: https://youtu.be/4lt7BtLEBA4

Onchain Video Link : https://ipfs.io/ipfs/bafybeicbhtshqaxdve5ia62xaqy265jahiwdcwtnctwfayx2sht4tpedte
